or ability to stop runnners recently, you'll go away again.<br><br>And yes, Paladins are the studiest, but they don't aggro well and don't have other tanking assets. In most guilds that raid, they are Healadins - a valuable clerical asset that does some tanking. Others who chose the tanking build <u>instead </u>of the clerical build tank, but not like Warirors. I don't bring up WoW because it's my dream tanking scheme. EQ actually is/was. 100% Primary Tank or hybrid - choose your poison. Those who wanted tanking superiority, chose Wariror and accepted inferiority in many areas outside of tanking. There is no Warrior puller build or clerical build, much less a TankPLUS build having two sets of abilities without the need to choose between them.<br><p>Message Edited by Battleblade-Xegony on <span class=date_text>03-07-2006</span> <span class=time_text>12:05 AM</span>	
