ecause you were provided a taunt button does not mean you are supposed to tank like a Wariror. Rangers have taunt buttons and they don't tank like knights. You are all three hybrids and gave up some tanking to get some non tanking abilities - you all got them in full measure.<span class="time_text"></span></p><p>Message Edited by Battleblade-Xegony on <span class=date_text>03-08-2006</span> <span class=time_text>05:14 AM</span>	
